Cards can be "player" cards or "extra" cards 

Every Player takes 23 cards (from all his available/collected cards)
    1x      Take Trainer - and put in the Trainer slot
    14x     Player Cards
    8x      Extre Cards

    Take from cards 11 cards:
    7x      Players
    4x      extra

    Rest of Extra cards and Players cards go to extra card/player slot

    Start Play with the 11 cards
    Position de player according to their skills (defending game column, middle game column, attacking game coliumn)

    Extra card will be played on the player, for instance yellow "card - extra card" will remove 2 points to the assigned player

    Weather cards will be be positioned in the weather card slot according their proprties

    

